(74, '20', 'What is the recommended dosage for Cefuroxime (Furotil)?', 'Dosage varies based on the infection and age group:\r\n\r\nAdults (13+ years): For most conditions like pharyngitis, bronchitis, and pneumonia, the dosage ranges from 250 mg to 500 mg twice daily for 5-14 days. For uncomplicated gonorrhea, a single 1000 mg dose is given.\r\nPediatric Patients (3 months to 12 years): The dosage typically ranges from 20 mg/kg/day to 30 mg/kg/day in two divided doses for 5-10 days.\r\nParenteral Use (Adults and Children): The dose can range from 750 mg to 1.5 g via intramuscular or intravenous injection, depending on the severity of the infection.', 'what-is-the-recommended-dosage-for-cefuroxime-furotil', NULL, '2024-10-08 16:29:57', '2024-10-08 16:29:57'),
